sentence: give me all nonstops , from new york city , to las vegas , that arrive on a sunday
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v0.flight_id||'"', v0.stops, '"'||v1.airport_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_name||'"',
 '"'||v0.flight_days||'"', v0.departure_time,
 v0.arrival_time, v0.time_elapsed FROM flight v0, airport_service v1,
 city v2, airport_service v3, city v4

AND (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code)

AND (((v0.flight_days IN (
SELECT v5.days_code FROM days v5

AND (((v0.departure_time > v0.arrival_time)
